aa(lp157
VInstead of starting with technology,
p158
aVthe team started with people and culture.
p159
aVSo if human need is the place to start,
p160
aVthen design thinking rapidly moves on to
p161
aVlearning by making.
p162
aVInstead of thinking about what to build,
p163
aVbuilding in order to think.
p164
aVNow, prototypes speed up the process of innovation,
p165
aVbecause it is only when we put our ideas out into the world
p166
aVthat we really start to understand their strengths and weaknesses.
