aa(lp170
VNow, much has been said and written about
p171
aVthe Aravind Eye Institute in Madurai, India.
p172
aVThey do an incredible job of serving very poor patients
p173
aVby taking the revenues from those who can afford to pay
p174
aVto cross-subsidize those who cannot.
p175
aVNow, they are very efficient,
p176
aVbut they are also very innovative.
p177
aVWhen I visited them a few years ago,
p178
aVwhat really impressed me was their willingness
p179
aVto prototype their ideas very early.
p180
aa(lp181
VThis is the manufacturing facility
p182
aVfor one of their biggest cost breakthroughs.
p183
aVThey make their own intraocular lenses.
p184
aVThese are the lenses that replace those
p185
aVthat are damaged by cataracts.
