VSo if human need is the place to start,
p201
aVand prototyping, a vehicle for progress,
p202
aVthen there are also some questions to ask about the destination.
p203
aVInstead of seeing its primary objective as consumption,
p204
aVdesign thinking is beginning to explore the potential of participation \u2014
p205
aVthe shift from a passive relationship
p206
aVbetween consumer and producer
p207
aVto the active engagement of everyone
p208
aVin experiences that are meaningful,
p209
aVproductive and profitable.
