aa(lp211
VSo I'd like to take the idea that Rory Sutherland talked about,
p212
aVthis notion that intangible things are worth perhaps more than physical things,
p213
aVand take that a little bit further and say that
p214
aVI think the design of participatory systems,
p215
aVin which many more forms of value
p216
aVbeyond simply cash
p217
aVare both created and measured,
p218
aVis going to be the major theme, not only for design,
p219
aVbut also for our economy as we go forward.
