aa(lp245
VWe can take this idea of participation
p246
aVperhaps to its logical conclusion
p247
aVand say that design may have its greatest impact
p248
aVwhen it's taken out of the hands of designers
p249
aVand put into the hands of everyone.
p250
aVNurses and practitioners at U.S. healthcare system
p251
aVKaiser Permanente
p252
aVstudy the topic of improving the patient experience,
p253
aVand particularly focused on the way that they exchange knowledge
p254
aVand change shift.
